    "bio": "n8n Template Creator | Automation Enthusiast | AI Integration Specialist\n\nI design powerful, easy-to-use automation templates that help businesses save time, boost efficiency, and scale smarter. Passionate about leveraging AI and no-code tools to solve real-world problems, I create workflows that simplify complex tasks and drive results.\n\nLet’s automate your workflow and unlock your productivity potential!\n",
